BRIDGE JOINS REUTERS... Now JOIN US!

On September 28, 2001, we were delighted to welcome into the Reuters family a variety of Bridge businesses including Bridge Information Systems in North America, StockVal, EJV, Bridge Trading Company, Bridge Trading Technologies, eBridge and the Bridge/CRB Index. Our primary commitment now is the stability and continuity of the Bridge products and the service we provide to you.  We are also excited about the potential these newly acquired capabilities give us to deliver best-of-breed solutions and enhanced connectivity for financial market professionals everywhere.

Join us in one of 11 cities in the US and Canada to learn more about our plans for Bridge products and the benefits our enhanced product offering will bring to you:

* BOSTON -- Thursday, October 11 -- Boston Harbor Hotel
* TORONTO -- Thursday, October 11 -- TSE Stock Market Place
* NEW YORK -- Monday, October 15 -- The Reuters Building @ 3XSQ
* SAN FRANCISCO -- Tuesday, October 16 -- The W Hotel
* VANCOUVER -- Tuesday, October 16 --  Sheraton Suites Le Soleil
* CHICAGO -- Wednesday, October 17 --  Union League Club of Chicago
* LOS ANGELES -- Thursday, October 18 -- Omni Los Angeles Hotel
* MONTREAL -- Thursday, October 18 -- Tsirco
* DENVER -- Tuesday, October 23 -- Loews Denver Hotel
* PHILADELPHIA -- Wednesday, October 24 -- The Ritz-Carlton
* HOUSTON -- Thursday, November 1 -- Hyatt Regency Houston

Come to hear a brief presentation, or, if you prefer, join us later for cocktails and hors d'oeuvres and a chance to meet with key executives to get your questions answered in an informal setting.  Pick the day/location that suits you best.

To register and for more details, just click here today.*

We look forward to seeing you soon.

Sincerely,

Stephen Pickett
Senior Vice President & Business Manager-West

